name: Php-shell
tagline: Brings PHP Shell to your browser
body:
### PHP Shell turns your browser into a PHP Shell

Note: Under early development. Only Chrome shell available (yet!).

To install, try and enjoy, please, refer to [the webstore](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/php-shell/hlpgiileennpalklffkdgjodnppfnccd) and start PHP'ing within your Devtools just now!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
